# (note: .feature-image-history.jsonl, .feature-image-pipeline.jsonl,
# and .feature-image-threads.jsonl are intentionally NOT gitignored —
# they hold the generation history, workflow-decision audit trail, and
# Phase 13 iteration conversation that Phase 11 fitness scoring and
# future analysis will compute from. Lose them = lose the design-system
# evolution.)
#
# Same for .editorial-draft-history.jsonl and .editorial-draft-pipeline.jsonl —
# intentionally tracked. They hold the review workflow's state machine,
# version history, and annotation log. The editorial-review Phase 12
# feedback signal (voice-drift aggregation) is computed from them.
